Caasimada waxay heshay muuqaal naqshad talyaani ah. Dadka reer Yurub waxay u isticmaaleen Asmara "si ay u tijaabiyaan naqshado cusub oo xagjir ah". [8] Markii la gaadhay 1930kii, Asmara waxaa loo yaqaan 'Piccola Roma' (Little Rome). [9] Maanta dhismayaal badan ayaa ka yimid asal ahaan talyaaniga, dukaamada ayaa weli leh magacyo Talyaani ah (tusaale, Bar Vittoria, Pasticceria moderna, Casa del formaggio, iyo Ferramenta).

